          "position": { "x": 40, "y": 40 },
          "size": { "width": 736, "height": 36 },
          "content": "How to Return Your Ballot",
          "flags": { "isMovable": true, "isEditable": true, "minQuantity": 1, "maxQuantity": 1 },
          "styles": { "fontSize": 30, "fontWeight": 700, "textAlign": "center" }
        },
        {
          "id": "ballot-return-body",
          "sourceToolId": "text-area",
          "type": "text",
          "position": { "x": 70, "y": 120 },
          "size": { "width": 676, "height": 420 },
          "content": "<p>Seal your completed ballot in the secrecy envelope, then place it in the return envelope.</p><ol><li>Sign and date the declaration.</li><li>Mail by Election Day or use an official drop box by 8:00 PM.</li><li>Track ballot status online with your voter ID.</li></ol><p><em>Local election office phone:</em> (555) 010-2300</p>",
          "flags": { "isMovable": true, "isEditable": true, "minQuantity": 1, "maxQuantity": 1 },
          "styles": { "fontSize": 19, "lineHeight": 1.5 }
        },
        {
          "id": "ballot-return-oath",
          "sourceToolId": "text-area",
          "type": "text",
          "position": { "x": 70, "y": 580 },
          "size": { "width": 676, "height": 180 },
          "content": "<p><strong>Voter Oath</strong></p><p>I declare under penalty of perjury that I am a qualified voter and that I completed this ballot personally.</p>",
          "flags": { "isMovable": true, "isEditable": true, "minQuantity": 1, "maxQuantity": 1 },
          "styles": { "fontSize": 18, "border": "1px solid #111827", "padding": "12px" }
